{"tid":1838471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(民意調查)一句講晒支唔支持醫護大罷工","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T05:29:17.000Z","uid":338612,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2b3db204666c1c0cf6fc9c6fd4ae99daa1eb18","tid":1838471,"uid":338612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"一句到尾<br />\n支持香港醫護大罷工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對香港醫護大罷工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共政府漠視香港市民安全<br />\n完全唔做防疫要醫護埋單<br />\n你地支唔支持醫護人員罷工抗議?<br />\n定係覺得醫生護士要為防疫不力埋單?要做condom?<br />\n<br />\n請幫手推post推到民意盡快浮到上水<br />\n因為醫護界罷工只有可能發生係未出現大量香港人中招之前,<br />\n當身邊有人中招你就可能會屌點解醫護唔救你<br />\n<br />\n宜家中招d垃圾蝗死唔死都唔緊要先罷到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推post唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f289c66606708b4fe1d42f6b534050ea8b50fd3c","tid":1838471,"uid":338612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手 p牌推唔到"},{"pid":"0c45c9ad7849dc93ecde19b51607979815a77dac","tid":1838471,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5a3d2485155346eb8ec35e079efaa964cae9d383","tid":1838471,"uid":338612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c45c9ad7849dc93ecde19b51607979815a77dac","tid":1838471,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":